         This is an enlarged view on a fragment of cDNA microarray. By calculation of the RED/GREEN ratio  for each spot (corresponding to one gene)it is possible to determine the concentration of mRNA (gene expression measure) from test and the reference conditions.
       </caption>
    </figure>
  <para id="flashDNA">
You can also refer to the comprehensive presentation of the <link url="http://www.bio.davidson.edu/courses/genomics/chip/chip.html">DNA-Microarray technology</link>
  </para>

